{
  "texts": [
    "In their study, Chi et al.",
    "described a scheme based on blockchain and a community detection algorithm to ensure the security of data sharing.",
    "The scheme was divided into four phases, including the initialization, identity authentication, signature and verification, and data sharing phases.",
    "A community detection algorithm was used to receive and analyze the label data of all clients and detect the community via cosine similarity and the K-medoids clustering algorithm and upload the community detection results to the blockchain network [27].Benil and Jasper created a blockchain-based EHR outsourcing scheme.",
    "The scheme eliminated duplicate EHR and reduced the space required for storage."
  ]
}